'''Fitbit'''（全名：Fitbit, Inc.）<ref name=":0" />是[[美國|美國]][[消費電子產品|消費電子產品]]和健身公司，總部位於[[加州|加州]][[舊金山|舊金山]]，主要產品包括{{tsl|en|Activity tracker|活動追蹤器}}、[[智慧型手錶|智慧型手錶]]和[[無線通訊|無線]][[可穿戴式智慧型產品|可穿戴式智慧型產品]]等。該公司原名Healthy Metrics Research，於2007年10月改為現名。<ref name="investor.fitbit.com"/>2019年，[[Google|Google]]宣布計畫以21億美元收購Fitbit<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/2019/11/01/775419131/google-buys-fitbit-for-2-1-billion-pledges-to-protect-health-data|title=Google Buys Fitbit For $2.1 Billion, Pledges To Protect Health Data|author=Paolo Zialcita|website=[[NPR|NPR]]|language=en|access-date=2019-11-03|archive-date=2019-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191103095528/https://www.npr.org/2019/11/01/775419131/google-buys-fitbit-for-2-1-billion-pledges-to-protect-health-data|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Google 以 21 億美元買下 Fitbit，正面對決 Apple Watch |url=https://technews.tw/2019/11/02/google-acquire-fitbit/ |accessdate=2021-02-03 |author=Cardin.Y |date=2019-11-02 |publisher=TechNews 科技新報 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809111640/https://technews.tw/2019/11/02/google-acquire-fitbit/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而該交易在美國及歐洲的監管機構批准後，於2021年1月完成。<ref name="cnbc complete">{{cite web | url = https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/14/google-closes-its-fitbit-acquisition.html | title = Google closes its Fitbit acquisition | first = Jessica | last = Bursztynsky | date = 2021-01-14 | access-date = 2021-01-14 | work = [[CNBC|CNBC]] | archive-date = 2021-01-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210129021928/https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/14/google-closes-its-fitbit-acquisition.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite web|last=Porter|first=Jon|date=2021-01-14|title=Google completes purchase of Fitbit|url=https://www.theverge.com/2021/1/14/22188428/google-fitbit-acquisition-completed-approved|access-date=2021-01-15|website=The Verge|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129234615/https://www.theverge.com/2021/1/14/22188428/google-fitbit-acquisition-completed-approved|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018 年 2 月，Fitbit 宣布將與阿迪達斯合作發布阿迪達斯品牌的 Fitbit Ionic。特別版 Ionic 於 2018 年 3 月 19 日發布。<ref name="mg21">{{Cite web |url=https://www.mg21.com/fitbit.html |title=可穿戴设备公司：FitBit, Inc.(FIT) |publisher=美股之家 |date=2021-07-10 |access-date=2021-07-11 |archive-date=2021-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210713033437/https://www.mg21.com/fitbit.html }}</ref>

2018 年 8 月，Blue Cross Blue Shield 協會宣布與 Fitbit 建立合作夥伴關係，其中 BCBS 將把 Fitbit 的可穿戴設備和健身追踪器納入其 Blue365 計劃。<ref name="mg21"/>

根據[[國際數據資訊|國際數據資訊]]（IDC）在2020年3月10日發表的報告，截至2019年，Fitbit是出貨量第五大的[[可穿戴式智能產品|可穿戴公司]]，同比增長14.8％<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.idc.com/getdoc.jsp?containerId=prUS46122120|title=Shipments of Wearable Devices Reach 118.9 Million Units in the Fourth Quarter and 336.5 Million for 2019, According to IDC|website=IDC: The premier global market intelligence company|access-date=2020-03-27|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114120031/https://www.idc.com/getdoc.jsp?containerId=prUS46122120|dead-url=no}}</ref>，僅次於[[小米集團|小米]]和[[蘋果公司|蘋果]]。而Fitbit的報告則顯示其已出售超過1億部設備，擁有2,800萬用戶。<ref>{{cite web |last1=O'Brien |first1=Matt |title=One big step: Google buys Fitbit for $2.1 billion |url=https://apnews.com/e5d41ca489514857af9f6faa154435bb |website=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |access-date=2019-11-20 |date=2019-11-01 |archive-date=2021-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114195439/https://apnews.com/e5d41ca489514857af9f6faa154435bb |dead-url=no }}</ref>

